message: >
  If this software is used in research, please cite it using the metadata below.
title: "Starter: Reusable Python Infrastructure Subsystems"
abstract: >
  Starter is a reusable Python foundation providing shared infrastructure
  subsystems for machine learning and research projects. It includes subsystems
  for configuration management (Hydra/OmegaConf), structured logging, experiment
  tracking, data profiling, artifact management, bootstrap orchestration, and
  hyperparameter search.
